<p>Domain registration costs $10 to $20 per year. Business email via Google Workspace adds $6 to $18 per user per month. A professional logo and brand identity through a freelancer runs $200 to $2,000.</p>
<p>Most first-year agencies launch with a $1,000 to $2,000 website and upgrade once revenue justifies the investment.</p>
