<h3>The Cash Reserve Rule</h3>
<p>Maintain 5 months of operating expenses in reserve at all times. For a lean agency, that is $4,000 to $5,000. For a small team agency, that is $60,000 to $70,000.</p>
<p>This reserve absorbs client churn, slow sales months, and unexpected costs. Agencies without a reserve make desperate decisions. Desperate decisions kill margins.</p>
